> > .. MP-BIOS bug: 8254 timer not connected to IO-APIC
> > ...trying to set up timer as ExtINT... failed
>                                ^^^^^^
> > ...tryng to set up timer as BP IRQ... failed
> > Kernel panic: IO APIC + timer doesn't work!
